---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
import Eyebrow from "../components/Eyebrow.astro";
import { site } from "../data/site";
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — Unicorn Fitness"
  description="How Unicorn Fitness collects and uses the information you share with us."
>
  <Section tight>
    <div style="max-width: 720px; margin-inline:auto; padding-block: var(--space-16);">
      <Eyebrow>Legal</Eyebrow>
      <h1 class="h-section" style="margin-top: var(--space-4); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <p class="body-sm" style="color: var(--ash); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
        {/* NOTE: accurately describes current site behaviour. Have this reviewed by a
           professional before relying on it for anything beyond the website itself —
           particularly if you later add analytics, accounts, or payment collection. */}
        This policy explains what information Unicorn Fitness collects through this website and how it's used.
      </p>

      <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap: var(--space-6);">
        <div>
          <h2 class="h-sub">What we collect</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">
            When you use the "Claim Your Free Trial Day" form, we ask for your name, phone number, what you're
            interested in, and an optional message. That's all — no account, no password, no payment details.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="h-sub">How it's used</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">
            Submitting the form opens WhatsApp with your details prefilled into a message addressed to
            Unicorn Fitness. The message is sent directly through WhatsApp — we don't store a copy of it on our
            servers, and it isn't shared with anyone outside Unicorn Fitness. WhatsApp's own privacy policy
            governs how that message is handled once it reaches WhatsApp.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="h-sub">How long we keep it</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">
            We don't hold a separate database of website enquiries — your message lives in the WhatsApp
            conversation between you and Unicorn Fitness, for as long as that conversation is useful to both of
            us. If you'd like us to delete it, tell us on WhatsApp and we will.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="h-sub">Your rights</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">
            You can ask us at any time what information we hold about you, ask us to correct it, or ask us to
            delete it. Message us on WhatsApp or call {site.phone} and we'll action it directly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="h-sub">Third party services</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">
            This site loads fonts from Google Fonts and an embedded Google Map on the contact page. Each of
            these may see your IP address as a normal part of serving that resource, the same as any website
            using them. Icons are served directly from this site rather than a third party.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="h-sub">Cookies & tracking</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">
            We don't currently run analytics, ads, or tracking cookies on this site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="h-sub">Grievance officer</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">
            {/* TODO(owner): India's IT Rules expect a named individual here, not just a
               phone number — replace with the designated grievance officer's name (and
               email, if you have one) before launch. */}
            For any privacy complaint or concern, contact Unicorn Fitness directly at
            <a href={site.phoneHref} class="btn--text"> {site.phone}</a> or on
            <a href="/contact" class="btn--text"> WhatsApp</a>. We aim to acknowledge concerns within a few days.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="h-sub">Contact us</h2>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-top: var(--space-3);">
            Questions about this policy? Reach us at <a href={site.phoneHref} class="btn--text">{site.phone}</a> or
            on <a href="/contact" class="btn--text">WhatsApp</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Base>
